    - key: Season.PaidPass.Desc
      translations:
      - "Unlock More Rewards\n<size=42><alpha=#C0><i>Activating now will immediately unlock </color><alpha=#FF><b>{tier}</b></color><alpha=#C0> rewards.</i></color></size>"
      - "報酬をさらにアンロック\n<size=42><alpha=#C0><i>有効化すると</color><alpha=#FF><b>{tier}</b></color><alpha=#C0>報酬を即アンロックできます。</i></color></size>"
      - "Débloque plus de récompenses\n<size=42><alpha=#C0><i>Activer maintenant débloquera immédiatement des récompenses </color><alpha=#FF><b>{tier}</b></color><alpha=#C0>.</i></color></size>"
      - "解锁更多奖励\n<size=42><alpha=#C0><i>现在激活，即可解锁</color><alpha=#FF><b>{tier}</b></color><alpha=#C0>奖励。</i></color></size>"
      - "解鎖更多獎勵\n<size=42><alpha=#C0><i>現在啟用將能立即解鎖</color><alpha=#FF><b>{tier}</b></color><alpha=#C0>獎勵。</i></color></size>"
      - "더 많은 보상을 해제하세요\n<size=42><alpha=#C0><i>지금 활성화 시 보상 </color><alpha=#FF><b>{tier}</b></color><alpha=#C0>개를 즉시 해제합니다.</i></color></size>"
      - "Buka Lebih Banyak Hadiah\n<size=42><alpha=#C0><i>Mengaktifkan sekarang akan segera membuka </color><alpha=#FF><b>{tier}</b></color><alpha=#C0> hadiah.</i></color></size>"
      - "Schalte mehr Belohnungen frei\n<size=42><alpha=#C0><i>Durch Aktivierung werden die </color><alpha=#FF><b>{tier}</b></color><alpha=#C0>Belohnungen</i></color></size> sofort freigeschaltet."
      - "Desbloquea más recompensas\n<size=42><alpha=#C0><i>Al activarlo ahora, se desbloquearán inmediatamente </color><alpha=#FF><b>{tier}</b></color><alpha=#C0> recompensas.</i></color></size>"
      - "Sblocca più ricompense\n<size=42><alpha=#C0><i>Attivalo subito per sbloccare immediatamente </color>le<alpha=#C0> ricompense</color> di classe <alpha=#FF><b>{tier}</b>.</i></color></size>"
      - "Desbloqueia mais recompensas\n<size=42><alpha=#C0><i>Ao ativar agora, desbloquearás imediatamente </color><alpha=#FF><b>{tier}</b></color><alpha=#C0> recompensas.</i></color></size>"
      - "Desbloqueie mais recompensas\n<size=42><alpha=#C0><i>Ativar agora desbloqueará imediatamente </color><alpha=#FF><b>{tier}</b></color><alpha=#C0> recompensas.</i></color></size>"
      - "Daha Fazla Ödülün Kilidini Aç\n<size=42><alpha=#C0><i>Şimdi etkinleştirmek, </color><alpha=#FF><b>{tier</b></color><alpha=#C0> ödüllerin kilidini anında açacaktır.</i></color></size>"
      - "Откройте другие награды\n<size=42><alpha=#C0><i>Активируйте и сразу же откройте награды за </color><alpha=#FF><b>{tier}</b></color><alpha=#C0>.</i></color></size>"
