    - key: MessagingSystem.Text.ThankYouPayers
      translations:
      - '<align="center"><b><size=125%><line-height=80%><color=#dd43e5>You make this possible!</color></b></line-height><br><size=100%>You made a purchase in the last 30 days and we wanted to thank you.</align>'
      - '<align="center"><b><size=125%><line-height=80%><color=#dd43e5>お客様のおかげで実現しました!</color></b></line-height><br><size=100%>過去 30 日間にご購入いただき、誠にありがとうございます。</align>'
      - '<align="center"><b><size=125%><line-height=80%><color=#dd43e5>C''est grâce à vous !</color></b></line-height><br><size=100%>Vous avez effectué un achat au cours des 30 derniers jours et nous tenons à vous remercier.</align>'
      - '<align="center"><b><size=125%><line-height=80%><color=#dd43e5>您让这一切成为可能！</color></b></line-height><br><size=100%>您在过去 30 天内进行了购买，我们想向您表示感谢。</align>'
      - '<align="center"><b><size=125%><line-height=80%><color=#dd43e5>您讓這一切成為可能！ </color></b></line-height><br><size=100%>您在過去 30 天內進行了購買，我們想向您表示感謝。 </align>'
      - '<align="center"><b><size=125%><line-height=80%><color=#dd43e5>여러분 덕분에 이것이 가능해졌습니다!</color></b></line-height><br><size=100%>지난 30일 이내에 구매를 하셨고, 감사의 말씀을 전하고 싶습니다.</align>'
      - '<align="center"><b><size=125%><line-height=80%><color=#dd43e5>Anda mewujudkannya!</color></b></line-height><br><size=100%>Anda melakukan pembelian dalam 30 hari terakhir dan kami ingin mengucapkan terima kasih.</align>'
      - '<align="center"><b><size=125%><line-height=80%><color=#dd43e5>Sie machen das möglich!</color></b></line-height><br><size=100%>Sie haben in den letzten 30 Tagen einen Kauf getätigt und wir möchten uns bei Ihnen bedanken.</align>'
      - '<align="center"><b><size=125%><line-height=80%><color=#dd43e5>¡Tú lo haces posible!</color></b></line-height><br><size=100%>Realizaste una compra en los últimos 30 días y queríamos agradecerte.</align>'
      - '<align="center"><b><size=125%><line-height=80%><color=#dd43e5>Tu rendi tutto questo possibile!</color></b></line-height><br><size=100%>Hai effettuato un acquisto negli ultimi 30 giorni e volevamo ringraziarti.</align>'
      - '<align="center"><b><size=125%><line-height=80%><color=#dd43e5>Você torna isso possível!</color></b></line-height><br><size=100%>Você fez uma compra nos últimos 30 dias e gostaríamos de agradecer.</align>'
      - '<align="center"><b><size=125%><line-height=80%><color=#dd43e5>Você torna isso possível!</color></b></line-height><br><size=100%>Você fez uma compra nos últimos 30 dias e gostaríamos de agradecer.</align>'
      - '<align="center"><b><size=125%><line-height=80%><color=#dd43e5>Bunu mümkün kılan sizsiniz!</color></b></line-height><br><size=100%>Son 30 gün içinde bir satın alma işlemi gerçekleştirdiniz ve size teşekkür etmek istedik.</align>'
      - '<align="center"><b><size=125%><line-height=80%><color=#dd43e5>Благодаря вам это стало возможным!</color></b></line-height><br><size=100%>Вы совершили покупку за последние 30 дней, и мы хотели бы поблагодарить вас.</align>'
    - key: MessagingSystem.Title.ThankYouPayers
      translations:
